  Scriptwriting with ChatGPT and Refining

In this video, I'm going to show you how to develop characters and write a script using ChatGPT. Again, these are just tools that can help you overcome creative roadblocks. A ChatGPT script will likely not be as good as a script created by a human, but when in the right hands, a ChatGPT-empowered screenwriting process can help you create incredible scripts.
